wn.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />人都會俾鱷魚咬架 收埋自己係屋企就無事架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80de508c7543898e711c9d7597dd4c2eeae93440","tid":1168371,"uid":24308,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T21:29:31.000Z","msg":"貓都要打格<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4546d1bf9812001d211edf3934ad84c61f67ccac","tid":1168371,"uid":108120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T06:21:20.000Z","msg":"搵個fb page黎睇 主要係勸養貓既人唔好比隻貓離開屋企 放隻貓出街後果一係就比其他動物捕食 一係就破壞自然生態"},{"pid":"0f77a805c1c5c626acd4023113250f16e87bd3b9","tid":1168371,"uid":99962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T06:32:06.000Z","msg":"好奇害死貓"}]}